{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4e794f897e","title":"关于转送张澜复信致邓小平电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f12ae1989b","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":24,"articleId":"4e794f897e"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"d457f21825","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓小平，当时任中共中央西南局第一书记。"},{"id":"7674ce1774","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指邓小平1951年1月8日关于西南局11、12两月工作情况给毛泽东并中央的报告。"},{"id":"f7f54c5ecf","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指张澜1951年1月24日给毛泽东的信。信中说：邓小平同志1月8日报告已详阅。关于退押进行情况，言之甚详，处理亦甚当。西南押租，系预防细户不能缴纳个租而为之预押，要到退细时才退押，实在是一种剥削。今天土地权收归国有，主个关系已不存在，当然应该退押。报告上说，等到退押浪潮过去，大部分退了的时候，及时转入清理，说服群众分别对待中小地主，对于确有困难的中小地主，多在“缓、少、不”三字上做文章，对顽固的则交法庭处理。将来能够切实审慎照此做是很好的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"878c2e33f5","type":"title","text":"关于转送张澜复信致邓小平电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e"},{"id":"d457f21825","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e"},{"id":"7674ce1774","type":"paragraph","text":"你一月八日报告我送给张表方先生看了，现将他的复信“转给你看。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e"},{"id":"f7f54c5ecf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e"},{"id":"b6afe60cb9","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e"},{"id":"28b5881583","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]张澜，字表方，当时任中国民主同盟中央主席、中央人民政府副主席。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e"}],"page":{"id":"6196b9d051","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"4e794f897e","start":73,"end":73}}}},"__N_SSG":true}